quran[8{c,v,t}:
22,65,kiya tum nahi dekhte ke jitni cheezein zameen mein hain ( sab ) khuda ne tumahray zeray farman kar rakhi hain aur kashtiyan ( bhi ) jo isi ke hukum se darya mein chalti hain. aur woh aasman ko thaamay rehta hai ke zameen par ( nah ) gur parre magar is ke hukum se. be shak khuda logon par nihayat shafqat karne wala meharban hai
22,66,aur wohi to hai jis ne tum ko hayaat bakhsh. phir tum ko maarta hai. phir tumhe zindah bhi kere ga. aur ensaan to bara na shukar hai
22,67,hum ne har aik aُmt ke liye aik Shariat muqarrar kar di hai jis par woh chaltay hain to yeh log tum se is amar mein jhagra nah karen aur tum ( logon ko ) apne perwar-digaar ki taraf bulatay raho. be shak tum seedhay raste par ho
22,68,aur agar yeh tum se jhagra karen to keh do ke jo amal tum karte ho khuda un se khoob waaqif hai
22,69,jin baton mein tum ikhtilaaf karte ho khuda tum mein qayamat ke roz un ka faisla kardey ga
22,70,kiya tum nahi jantay ke jo kuch aasman aur zameen mein hai khuda is ko jaanta hai. yeh ( sab kuch ) kitaab mein ( likha howa ) hai. be shak yeh sab khuda ko aasaan hai
22,71,aur ( yeh log ) khuda ke siwa aisi cheezon ki ibadat karte hain jin ki is ne koi sanad nazil nahi farmai aur nah un ke paas is ki koi Daleel hai. aur zaalmon ka koi bhi madadgaar nahi hoga
22,72,aur jab un ko hamari ayatain parh kar sunai jati to ( un ki shakal baggar jati hai aur ) tum un ke cheharon mein saaf tor par na khushi ( ke assaar ) dekhte ho. qareeb hotay hain ke jo log un ko hamari ayatain parh kar sunaate hain un par hamla kar dein. keh do ke mein tum ko is se bhi buri cheez batau? woh dozakh ki aag hai. jis ka khuda ne kafiroon se wadakiya hai. aur woh bura thikana hai
